{"tid":2439231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸克倫解放軍宣佈與示威民眾同行 保護民眾免被軍方攻擊","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T11:53:18.000Z","uid":391580,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2c41907e40540a1e0ffa019f0a31842cd1ce8748","tid":2439231,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"【緬甸中文網訊】德林達依省消息，克倫第4旅的士兵，在德林達依省土瓦市轄區內，為民眾的示威抗議活動提供安保工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n克倫解放軍士兵在示威隊伍前隨同遊行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0xuoN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0xuoN9.jpg&h=a3763580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfhFvta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfhFvta.jpg&h=aa53c8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pR5oteR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpR5oteR.jpg&h=67f4b3ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxRnJOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxRnJOb.jpg&h=c7d2b40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Njy9oOd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjy9oOd.jpg&h=74925947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>多名宣布參加CDM的警員<br />\n<br />\n尋求民眾的庇護<br />\n</strong><br />\n【緬甸中文網訊】孟邦消息，3月5日下午3點30分，有6名警員宣布加入到CDM（反軍政府示威）中。但由於擔心安全問題，因此通過街區/村莊管理員的聯繫，進入到克倫軍控區直通縣第1旅齋托鎮KNLA第3營，尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，6名警員分別是茂散郭郭茂、茂欣郭登、茂千敏昂、茂欣郭倫、茂昂別漂茂、茂維漂。他們6人平時就經常聯繫，軍方接管政權後，他們互相聯繫討論，最終作出決定，參與到CDM（反軍政府示威）中。<br />\n<br />\n此外，3月6日午間12點左右，參與到CDM（反軍政府示威）的登扎亞警局的警員茂昂博，攜妻子進入到克倫直通縣齋托鎮KNLA第3營尋求庇護。 3月7日，在若開邦任職參加CDM的警員茂函敏昂，抵達KNLA第3營尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sr3dQtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsr3dQtS.jpg&h=ba92614d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孟邦毛淡棉鎮總務局副局長參加CDM<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHzpcHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHzpcHm.jpg&h=7c74d53b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【緬甸中文網訊】孟邦消息，3月6日起，毛淡棉鎮區總務局副局長吳謬奈，依據自己的個人意願參與到CDM（反政府示威）中。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，吳謬奈在聯邦政府辦公室部下屬的總務局工作已有34年時間，曾獲得過優秀公務員稱號。<br />\n<br />\n吳謬奈表示，參加CDM，不是辭職，是與民眾站在同一立場。同時，參加和平示威，完全是依據自己的個人意願，並沒有受到任何人、任何政黨、任何組織的唆使，與家屬、朋友、同事無關。"},{"pid":"8c635dc02ce050fe1dd790271280df9da089b993","tid":2439231,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"緬甸聯邦有冇機會解體"},{"pid":"d955e40ee1ca7d05688cbc8d6e95c64a6f41fe40","tid":2439231,"uid":83910,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:00:39.000Z","msg":"睇錯中国解放軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a88ed64b514d6f6bde1a44d798bf087da4fd38","tid":2439231,"uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d955e40ee1ca7d05688cbc8d6e95c64a6f41fe40","tid":2439231,"uid":83910,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:00:39.000Z","msg":"睇錯中国解放軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:00:58.000Z","msg":"咁就真係要驗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3823f704a0ed572540264b203c28b6999893bfc5","tid":2439231,"uid":333312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"希望佢哋平安啦"},{"pid":"cad9f64792ee1679d3e30199d4cb6e1152687098","tid":2439231,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:02:53.000Z","msg":"諗起rambo <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ki